OL,3,CUCU calls off strike at Cardiff
OL,4,CUniversity as job cuts on hold
OL,6,FPlanned strike action at Cardiff
OL,7,FUniversity has been called off at the
OL,8,Flast minute after an agreement there
OL,9,Fwill be no compulsory job cuts this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FMembers of the University and College
OL,13,FUnion agreed to suspend their plans in
OL,14,Fa meeting held today.
OL,16,FBut the agreement does not rule out
OL,17,Fredundancies after this academic year.
