OL,3,CUCU calls off strike at Cardiff
OL,4,CUniversity as job cuts on hold
OL,6,FEarlier this week, the University and
OL,7,FCollege Union (UCU) agreed to suspend
OL,8,Fthe industrial action planned for the
OL,9,F1st of May to meet with the
OL,10,FUniversity's Executive Board.
OL,12,FThe University has ruled out
OL,13,Fcompulsory redundancies for some staff
OL,14,Fbefore the end of this year, in
OL,15,Fexchange for the suspension of
OL,16,Findustrial action.
OL,18,FIn March UCU members voted to Strike
OL,19,Fover proposed job cuts at the
OL,20,FUniversity.
