OL,3,CUCU calls off strike at Cardiff
OL,4,CUniversity as job cuts on hold
OL,6,FAt the time the UCU said "83% (of
OL,7,Fmembers) backed strike action and 86%
OL,8,Fbacked action short of strike up to
OL,9,Fand including an assessment boycott".
OL,11,FIt was in response to proposals made
OL,12,Fby Vice-Chancellor Professor Wendy
OL,13,FLarner in January to no longer provide
OL,14,Fcourses in Ancient History, Modern
OL,15,FLanguages and Translation, Music,
OL,16,FNursing, and Religion and Theology.
OL,18,FIt left staff concerned that 400
OL,19,Fpeople could lose their jobs.
