OL,3,CUCU calls off strike at Cardiff
OL,4,CUniversity as job cuts on hold
OL,6,FThe Vice Chancellor had said
OL,7,F"difficult decisions" needed to be
OL,8,Ftaken.
OL,10,FAt the time a 90 day consultation
OL,11,Fperiod on the cuts was opened. In a
OL,12,Fjoint Statement between the UCU,
OL,13,FUniversity Executive Board, Unite, and
OL,14,FUnison published yesterday (30th
OL,15,FApril) they said "valid questions have
OL,16,Fbeen raised about the outcome of the
OL,17,Fconsultation process, and when staff
OL,18,Fwill be informed of those outcomes."
