OL,3,CUCU calls off strike at Cardiff
OL,4,CUniversity as job cuts on hold
OL,6,FThey've now committed to publish an
OL,7,Finterim timetable next week, showing
OL,8,Fwhat happens between the end of the
OL,9,Fconsultation and the Council meeting
OL,10,Fon 17 June. They say that is when
OL,11,Fthere will be a definitive update on
OL,12,Fthe impact on staff.
OL,14,FIn that statement, the UCU, University
OL,15,FExecutive Board, Unite, and Unison say
OL,16,F"we want to recognise the very real
OL,17,Fhuman impact that the Academic Future
OL,18,Fproject has had, and the level of
OL,19,Fanxiety felt more broadly across the
OL,20,Facademic and professional services.
