OL,3,CUCU calls off strike at Cardiff
OL,4,CUniversity as job cuts on hold
OL,6,F"Again we have committed to working in
OL,7,Fpartnership together to assess the
OL,8,Fsteps that we can take to ensure that
OL,9,Fwe are looking after the health and
OL,10,Fwellbeing of our staff."
OL,12,FAlthough UCU spokesperson described
OL,13,Ftoday's development as a "big
OL,14,Fvictory", the union warned that "over
OL,15,F1000 jobs still remain at risk and
OL,16,Fwhile the University partially
OL,17,Freversed plans to end nursing
OL,18,Fprovision, other Schools are still set
OL,19,Ffor closure."
