OL,3,CUCU calls off strike at Cardiff
OL,4,CUniversity as job cuts on hold
OL,6,FA Cardiff UCU Spokesperson commented
OL,7,F"our members are still deeply unhappy
OL,8,Fwith the restructuring process, and
OL,9,Fthe way it is being delivered. For
OL,10,Fthat reason, we've also decided to
OL,11,Fseek to renew our industrial action
OL,12,Fmandate when the current one expires.
OL,14,F"We truly welcome the new partnership-
OL,15,Fled approach the University has
OL,16,Fcommitted to, and we look forward to
OL,17,Fworking much more closely together
OL,18,Fthan we've been able to so far. We
OL,19,Fwill be releasing a joint statement
OL,20,Fregarding the agreement in due course."
